### 3.5 AgentCommissionLog
Tracks the earnings for insurance agents.
| Variable | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `AgentId` | int | The agent receiving the commission. |
| `PolicyId` | int | The policy that generated the commission. |
